Learn more about how Links work in our </span></span><a href="https://www.figma.com/community/file/832634397112145954" class="css-4rbku5 css-1dbjc4n r-1loqt21 r-1471scf r-1otgn73 r-1i6wzkk r-lrvibr"><span data-key="c2fe052c9897434a9fc8edb8cc3047bb" data-rnw-int-class="nearest_257-12458_259-12459-237__"><span data-key="b034169c604e40bbae2e58c85762c44d"><span data-offset-key="b034169c604e40bbae2e58c85762c44d:0">Links playground file</span></span></span></a><span key="383c3e3459684e0c96aa76df4189cee3"><span offset-key="383c3e3459684e0c96aa76df4189cee3:0">.</span></span>

<span key="96c5f8633daf4e139624758711aab7b6"><span offset-key="96c5f8633daf4e139624758711aab7b6:0">Copy links to Files, Pages, and Frames</span></span>

<span key="a19bed9dac544086a6baec80fb165507"><span offset-key="a19bed9dac544086a6baec80fb165507:0">Create navigation links to pages and frames within a large file, or link out to other Figma files and prototypes.</span></span>

<span key="2202dcff4b3a4710b58508664a7a21e7"><span offset-key="2202dcff4b3a4710b58508664a7a21e7:0">To find the link for your destination:</span></span>

## 

<span key="d58f44c2609d4e9d8a7ed1ca5f82fc1b"><span offset-key="d58f44c2609d4e9d8a7ed1ca5f82fc1b:0">File</span></span>

1.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">1.</span>
    <span key="e2e13bdd85b541fc84a07d687ddef668"><span offset-key="e2e13bdd85b541fc84a07d687ddef668:0">Open the file in the Editor.</span></span>

2.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">2.</span>
    <span key="2f89d5272981458083f1ac08de1b1c49"><span offset-key="2f89d5272981458083f1ac08de1b1c49:0">Click the </span>**Share**<span offset-key="2f89d5272981458083f1ac08de1b1c49:2"> button and set </span></span><a href="https://help.figma.com/hc/en-us/articles/360040531773" class="css-4rbku5 css-1dbjc4n r-1loqt21 r-1471scf r-1otgn73 r-1i6wzkk r-lrvibr"><span data-key="4e9633e033ce455b829d262c45ac07b7" data-rnw-int-class="nearest_257-12458_259-12459-237__"><span data-key="92aae01ebb844820ba9264d18377d6ac"><span data-offset-key="92aae01ebb844820ba9264d18377d6ac:0">Link Sharing permissions</span></span></span></a><span key="75a4564fa0d447ef98291cbc37f447f3"><span offset-key="75a4564fa0d447ef98291cbc37f447f3:0">.</span></span>

3.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">3.</span>
    <span key="3157844941804a72a4aced88726ba5ee"><span offset-key="3157844941804a72a4aced88726ba5ee:0">Click </span>**Copy Link**<span offset-key="3157844941804a72a4aced88726ba5ee:2"> to copy the URL to your clipboard:</span></span>

## 

<span key="07073eb9597449efa38685ffc4900580"><span offset-key="07073eb9597449efa38685ffc4900580:0">Prototype</span></span>

1.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">1.</span>
    <span key="3582dde68776498db4082311a2a93fb1"><span offset-key="3582dde68776498db4082311a2a93fb1:0">Open the file in the Editor.</span></span>

2.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">2.</span>
    <span key="869e880d3971479fb57f998abd20788f"><span offset-key="869e880d3971479fb57f998abd20788f:0">Click the </span>**Present**<span offset-key="869e880d3971479fb57f998abd20788f:2"> button to open the prototype in </span></span><a href="https://help.figma.com/hc/en-us/articles/360040318013" class="css-4rbku5 css-1dbjc4n r-1loqt21 r-1471scf r-1otgn73 r-1i6wzkk r-lrvibr"><span data-key="248d89bed67441f899282d3fe38b681f" data-rnw-int-class="nearest_257-12458_259-12459-237__"><span data-key="7c2dee23a2db4c5ab4319058b83442f7"><span data-offset-key="7c2dee23a2db4c5ab4319058b83442f7:0">presentation view</span></span></span></a><span key="ad95ae6e76fc404bb3e7ce4e3ddb9f7f"><span offset-key="ad95ae6e76fc404bb3e7ce4e3ddb9f7f:0">.</span></span>

3.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">3.</span>
    <span key="e8e008012e684ba0af1811259866cd77"><span offset-key="e8e008012e684ba0af1811259866cd77:0">Click the </span>**Share Prototype**<span offset-key="e8e008012e684ba0af1811259866cd77:2"> button and set </span></span><a href="https://help.figma.com/hc/en-us/articles/360040531773" class="css-4rbku5 css-1dbjc4n r-1loqt21 r-1471scf r-1otgn73 r-1i6wzkk r-lrvibr"><span data-key="d883b2b939764fb8b46a6367e51c605d" data-rnw-int-class="nearest_257-12458_259-12459-237__"><span data-key="4369ab1400514e91b9780744dcf6e782"><span data-offset-key="4369ab1400514e91b9780744dcf6e782:0">Link Sharing permissions</span></span></span></a><span key="4b748bb3073a48749d563771f2c2dea2"><span offset-key="4b748bb3073a48749d563771f2c2dea2:0">.</span></span>

4.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">4.</span>
    <span key="be9369e096f04fe485aea620996baaa6"><span offset-key="be9369e096f04fe485aea620996baaa6:0">Click </span>**Copy Link**<span offset-key="be9369e096f04fe485aea620996baaa6:2"> to copy the URL to your clipboard.</span></span>

## 

<span key="9edf22c9995a41f982fde67e8a8e7104"><span offset-key="9edf22c9995a41f982fde67e8a8e7104:0">Page</span></span>

1.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">1.</span>
    <span key="68945ddf921f4d2197e48c6beb2f9b58"><span offset-key="68945ddf921f4d2197e48c6beb2f9b58:0">Open the Layers panel and expand the page list.</span></span>

2.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">2.</span>
    <span key="86c1af8d715541aba9292556b851aba0"><span offset-key="86c1af8d715541aba9292556b851aba0:0">Right-click on the page name and select </span>**Copy Link**<span offset-key="86c1af8d715541aba9292556b851aba0:2">:</span></span>

## 

<span key="40f526e127e244d083fa92727a429090"><span offset-key="40f526e127e244d083fa92727a429090:0">Frame</span></span>

1.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">1.</span>
    <span key="1fa9969f78f3494e9d76a4259a92c5c7"><span offset-key="1fa9969f78f3494e9d76a4259a92c5c7:0">Right-click on the Frame in the canvas or Layers Panel.</span></span>

2.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">2.</span>
    <span key="ce440a2508294234844a645d0d170b7c"><span offset-key="ce440a2508294234844a645d0d170b7c:0">Go to </span>**Copy/Paste**<span offset-key="ce440a2508294234844a645d0d170b7c:2"> > </span>**Copy Link**<span offset-key="ce440a2508294234844a645d0d170b7c:4">.</span></span>

<span key="e52db1ead7c64c399c69c2fc628daf4e"><span offset-key="e52db1ead7c64c399c69c2fc628daf4e:0">Once copied, you can create a text layer and use it as a link to a page, file, frame, or prototype.</span></span>

<span key="c5a4bd7fecd94caca1f4225455bf2d65"><span offset-key="c5a4bd7fecd94caca1f4225455bf2d65:0">Tip! If you're using Figma in the browser, you can copy a link to the selected object from the browser's address bar.</span></span>

<span key="4896d8d1579249f18bd13cc96b762e0c"><span offset-key="4896d8d1579249f18bd13cc96b762e0c:0">Interact with links</span></span>

## 

<span key="f273dfa7d3d6425e8eabb9b63b8bb707"><span offset-key="f273dfa7d3d6425e8eabb9b63b8bb707:0">Preview or follow a link</span></span>

1.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">1.</span>
    <span key="5eae4e3368434462ad0e42d31a3a77c3"><span offset-key="5eae4e3368434462ad0e42d31a3a77c3:0">Hover over the linked text to preview the link.</span></span>

2.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">2.</span>
    <span key="f674bde8889f450da9df023bcc1978eb"><span offset-key="f674bde8889f450da9df023bcc1978eb:0">Click </span>**Open Link**<span offset-key="f674bde8889f450da9df023bcc1978eb:2"> to follow the link:</span></span>

3.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">3.</span>
    <span key="0570a27c774742dfb246caa978243620"><span offset-key="0570a27c774742dfb246caa978243620:0">What happens when you follow the linked text will depend on the type of link:</span></span>

    -   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

        <span key="9fa52d4b63c045249e494daa2b53133f">**Figma file or prototype:**<span offset-key="9fa52d4b63c045249e494daa2b53133f:1"> Figma will open links to other Figma files and prototypesâ€”or frames and pages within themâ€”in a new tab.</span></span>

    -   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

        <span key="68cfcdb8129b415fbe21c666aae4e074">**Page or frame:**<span offset-key="68cfcdb8129b415fbe21c666aae4e074:1"> Figma will take you to the page or frame in the current file.</span></span>

    -   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

        <span key="ced2e46dc7d74e148908a6c5ec0e2201">**External website:**<span offset-key="ced2e46dc7d74e148908a6c5ec0e2201:1"> Figma will open all external links in a new tab. The first time you open a link, you'll need to confirm that you're leaving Figma.</span></span>

<span key="1781df2c9c7a4f31a8c20fac90e985e9"><span offset-key="1781df2c9c7a4f31a8c20fac90e985e9:0">Edit or delete a link</span></span>

1.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">1.</span>
    <span key="1d5bd7deaf00452a9bb1c5e7918e4c28"><span offset-key="1d5bd7deaf00452a9bb1c5e7918e4c28:0">Hover over the linked text.</span></span>

2.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">2.</span>
    <span key="334c8afcc9f04af786170a55cefd58f7"><span offset-key="334c8afcc9f04af786170a55cefd58f7:0">Click </span>**Edit**<span offset-key="334c8afcc9f04af786170a55cefd58f7:2"> to make changes.</span></span>

3.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">3.</span>
    <span key="e569e328adf0406e83423fffbbe36777"><span offset-key="e569e328adf0406e83423fffbbe36777:0">Update the URL or click the detach icon to remove the link:</span></span>
